{"tid":927351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★環保吖嗱！口渴男攜水桶取免費水","createTime":"2018-12-04T06:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T08:12:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4b78cb9309d7771a12b7c24eb54edd0eeb7e4a5f","tid":927351,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181204/photo/bkn-20181204133931602-1204_00822_001_01b.jpg?20181204135110\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181204%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181204133931602-1204_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20181204135110&h=44c4f3af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日(4日)有網民分享一名男子於商場出動加大版「水樽」在水機前取水的照片，令看過照片的網民不禁諷刺說，「真係咁口渴？」<br />\n<br />\n從照片可見，該名「口渴男」提着容量估計有4至5公升的水桶，在水機取水。在水機附近坐着數名市民，但「口渴男」不以為然，態度自若，照片所見其水桶內只有小量食水，距離載滿尚有一段時間。「口渴男」身穿風衫，孭起背囊及腳踏行山鞋，憑其衣着及裝備，不排是準備郊遊，又或提供多人飲用，才取用大量食水。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181204/bkn-20181204133931602-1204_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181204%2Fbkn-20181204133931602-1204_00822_001.html&d=NYmES5WDJcQ8v5dh30qlY%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=d8ba9a25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181204/bkn-20181204133931602-1204_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"cb211af8ac63a074794038c2806e3a3d14d2d7d1","tid":927351,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:14:04.000Z","msg":"零成本 why not"},{"pid":"0d7b445ccfe016dd10a6eafbc246430f07a6c7cf","tid":927351,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:14:34.000Z","msg":"NB"},{"pid":"93f9e5a68dd60bb281002f12e4c9c8c67989fda6","tid":927351,"uid":87780,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:15:53.000Z","msg":"大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8181af5364ca3850625f358bd19ad90e3b31f